This project uses GNU autotools.

To install the scripts under /usr/local (scripts will go in the "bin"
subdirectory):

    ./configure
    make
    make install

To install under $HOME/local:

    ./configure --prefix="$HOME/local"
    make
    make install

To install using GNU stow under $HOME/local:

    ./configure --prefix="$HOME/local/stow/shell-toolbox"
    make
    make install
    cd "$HOME/local/stow"
    stow shell-toolbox

